<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 26. Epitranus inops Steffan (female) A head (frontal view) B lower part of face showing frontal lobe (frontal view) C antennal pedicel and flagellum D mesoscutellum and propodeum (dorsal view)." , "Figure 12. Epitranus subinops Soliman & Gadallah, sp. nov. (holotype female) A propodeum and metasoma (dorsal view) B head including antennal scape and mesosoma (lateral view) D fore wing (parts of wing membrane and MV and STV magnified)." , "Figure 10. Epitranus subinops Soliman & Gadallah, sp. nov. (holotype female) A, B, C habitus (lateral, dorsal and ventral views respectively)." , "Figure 27. Epitranus inops Steffan (female) A fore wing (parts of wing membrane and MV and STV magnified) B, C hind leg, excluding coxa (outer and ventral views respectively) D metasoma (dorsal view)." , "Figure 25. Epitranus inops Steffan (female) A, B habitus (lateral and dorsal views respectively)." , "Figure 11. Epitranus subinops Soliman & Gadallah, sp. nov. (holotype female) A head (frontal view) B lower part of face showing frontal lobe (frontal view) C head and pronotum (dorsal view) D antennal pedicel and flagellum E head and mesosoma (dorsal view)." , "Figure 13. Epitranus subinops Soliman & Gadallah, sp. nov. (holotype female) A, B hind leg, excluding coxa (outer and ventral views respectively) C metasoma (ventral view)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/467107" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/467087" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/467104" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/467088" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/467108" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/467090" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/467089" .

